    Class Description
    ArrayListConcat
    An ArrayListConcat is a SimpleAggregateFunction that concatenates ArrayLists together.
    ComparableMax
    An ComparableMax is a SimpleAggregateFunction that takes in Comparables and calculates the maximum comparable.
    ComparableMin
    An ComparableMin is a SimpleAggregateFunction that takes in Comparables and calculates the minimum comparable.
    First
    An First is a SimpleAggregateFunction that assumes the value will never change and just returns the first non null value it gets.
    FreqMapAggregator
    An FreqMapAggregator is a SimpleAggregateFunction that takes in FreqMaps and merges the frequencies together.
    IntegerFreqMapAggregator Deprecated
    use FreqMap with FreqMapAggregator.
    Max
    An Max is a SimpleAggregateFunction that takes in Numbers of the same type and calculates the maximum.
    Min
    An Min is a SimpleAggregateFunction that takes in Numbers of the same type and calculates the minimum.
    NumericAggregateFunction
    An NumericAggregateFunction is a SimpleAggregateFunction that takes in Numbers of the same type and processes the number in some way.
    Product
    An Min is a SimpleAggregateFunction that takes in Numbers of the same type and calculates the product.
    SetAggregator<T>
    An SetAggregator is a SimpleAggregateFunction that combines Sets.
    StringConcat
    An StringConcat is a SimpleAggregateFunction that takes in Strings and concatenates them together.
    Sum
    An Min is a SimpleAggregateFunction that takes in Numbers of the same type and calculates the sum.
